| **Executive IT Leadership** | [cite_start]CIO, CTO, COO, Head of IT, Head of Technology [cite: 94, 96] | [cite_start]Driving business objectives through IT strategy; reducing risk of failed transformations; ensuring ROI on tech investments[cite: 94]. |
| **IT Operations Manager** | [cite_start]Director of IT Ops, Head of IT Infrastructure, Manager of IT Service Delivery [cite: 38-41] | [cite_start]Oversees infrastructure and team; makes decisions on system changes and resource deployment[cite: 5, 6]. |
